contentrichtext.text: '''GFI''' may refer to: * [[Game Factory Interactive]], a Russian-Ukrainian video game developer * [[GFI Software]], a computer security software company * [[Global Financial Integrity]], a think tank based in Washington, DC. * ''[[Go4It]]'', a children's magazine programme on BBC Radio 4 * Gross [[Fixed investment|Fixed Investment]], an economic concept * Ground Fault Interrupter, a type of [[residual-current device]] * [[GFI Group]], provides wholesale brokerage, electronic execution and trading support products to institutional clients. {{disambig}} [[de:GFI]]
